# K8s Manifests Conventions

## CloudNativePG Cluster

```yaml
apiVersion: postgresql.cnpg.io/v1
kind: Cluster
metadata:
  name: pg-{app}
  namespace: puchi-db
spec:
  instances: 1
  imageName: ghcr.io/cloudnative-pg/postgresql:18.0
  storage:
    size: 10Gi
    storageClass: local-path
  bootstrap:
    initdb:
      database: {db_name}
      owner: {username}
      secret:
        name: pg-{app}-secret
```

## Backend Deployment

Mỗi service có:
- ConfigMap: `{service}-config` chứa config.yaml (server, data, auth)
- Deployment: image `ghcr.io/puchidemy/puchi-{service}:latest`
- Service: `{service}-service` (ClusterIP:8000)
- Ports: HTTP 8000, gRPC 9000

Auth config trong ConfigMap:
```yaml
auth:
  supertokens:
    connection_uri: "http://st-core.puchi-infra.svc.cluster.local:3567"
    api_key: "change-in-production-please"
    cookie_domain: "puchi.io.vn"
    cookie_secure: true
  public_paths:
    - /auth
    - /v1/health
    - /v1/healthz
```

## Frontend Deployment

```yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: web
  namespace: puchi-frontend
spec:
  containers:
    - env:
      - name: NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL
        value: "https://puchi.io.vn"
      - name: NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL
        value: "https://api.puchi.io.vn"
      - name: SUPERTOKENS_CONNECTION_URI
        value: "http://st-core-svc.puchi-infra.svc.cluster.local:3567"
```

## Envoy Gateway

### GatewayClass → Gateway
```yaml
apiVersion: gateway.networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: GatewayClass  # name: envoy-gateway
kind: Gateway       # name: puchi-gateway, listener HTTP:80
```

### SecurityPolicy (CORS + ext_auth)
```yaml
apiVersion: gateway.envoyproxy.io/v1alpha1
kind: SecurityPolicy
spec:
  targetRefs:
    - group: gateway.networking.k8s.io
      kind: HTTPRoute
      name: puchi-api-routes
  cors:
    allowOrigins: ["https://puchi.io.vn", "http://localhost:3000"]
    allowCredentials: true
  extAuth:
    http:
      backendRef: st-core-svc.puchi-infra:3567
      path: /session/verify
      headersToBackend: [cookie, authorization]
```

### HTTPRoute
```yaml
apiVersion: gateway.networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: HTTPRoute
spec:
  parentRefs:
    - name: puchi-gateway
  rules:
    - matches:
      - path:
          type: PathPrefix
          value: /core
      backendRefs:
        - name: core-service
          namespace: puchi-backend
          port: 8000
```

## Supertokens Deployment

```yaml
apiVersion: v1
kind: Service  # st-core-svc, NodePort 30567, target 3567
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment  # st-core, image supertokens/supertokens-postgresql:11.3
  env:
    - POSTGRESQL_CONNECTION_URI
    - API_KEYS
```

## Garage buckets

Tạo bucket qua Garage v2 admin API:

```bash
curl -X POST -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"globalAlias":"puchi-{bucket}"}' \
  http://{garage}:3903/v2/CreateBucket
```

## NATS streams

Tạo stream với subject prefix `puchi.*`:

```bash
nats str add puchi-{name} \
  --subjects "puchi.{domain}.>" \
  --storage file \
  --max-bytes=1GB
```

## Labels

- Tất cả resource gán label `app: puchi`
- Namespace pattern: `puchi-{env}` (puchi-db, puchi-infra, puchi-backend, puchi-frontend)
